    <skos:editorialNote>This file contains the 200811 version of CGI Convention Code list; use to specify the convention used for reporting the orientation of a planar feature. Used in CGI_PlanarOrientation, is enumeration in GeoSciML XML schema. This list is for information purposes.</skos:editorialNote>
